            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國2026年經濟成長目標設在4.5%-5% 大規模刺激措施出台可能性回落",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國2026年經濟成長目標設在4.5%-5% 大規模刺激措施出台可能性回落\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VpdwB.ah1nhGsog0BvGkMA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/8f8c00d0-1830-11f1-b8ff-38eef2057790\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國2026年經濟成長目標設在4.5%-5% 大規模刺激措施出台可能性回落</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B2026%E5%B9%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E8%A8%AD%E5%9C%A84-5-5-%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%88%BA%E6%BF%80%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%B0%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-000645606.html",
