        {
            "title": "美國貨幣市場基金資產升至紀錄新高8.27萬億美元 投資者湧向現金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著伊朗戰爭引發廣泛避險資金流入，美國貨幣市場基金總資產升至8.271萬億美元，創紀錄新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Crane Data LLC最新數據，截至3月3日當周，約490億美元流入貨幣市場基金。其中，僅周二單日就流入了約185億美元，當天美國和以色列對伊朗發動打擊的影響在市場持續發酵。今年以來，資金淨流入規模已超過1620億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「確實出現了奔向現金的情況，」道明證券策略師Jan Nevruzi表示，指出近幾周美國國債殖利率下跌。「再觀察幾天資金流向。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c13cdcf0-e216-37bd-b3b7-ad63ffece4bb-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BtY_9FGG.HanMgSAAPY2bQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a239b041b68212e7ca3decac04c3f501\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">快速演變的中東衝突加劇投資者焦慮，強化了配置避險資產的理由，尤其是現金。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「別忘了，聯儲會未來政策、美國經濟以及地緣政治都充滿不確定性 —— 這種整體偏負面的氛圍往往會促使投資者轉向更安全的避風港，」Federated Hermes全球流動性市場首席投資官Deborah Cunningham表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我相信其中一部分可以歸因於風險偏好下降和資金轉向優質資產，」德意志銀行策略師Steven Zeng表示，「但我也要指出，我們正處於報稅季，貨幣市場基金資產理應受益於退稅資金。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德意志銀行稱，今年退稅規模高出約10%，提振了資金流入。預計獲得退稅的納稅人往往更早報稅，收到的現金通常會回流貨幣市場基金。而資金流出通常要到3月和4月才會顯現，因為需要補稅的納稅人往往會等到臨近4月15日截止日才報稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Money Fund Assets Rise to Record $8.27 Trillion in Dash for Cash</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%988-27%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%B9%A7%E5%90%91%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91-195726227.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 09:12:34",
