        {
            "title": "中國2026年中央預算中國防支出成長7% 增速降至2022年以來最低",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國2026年中央預算中的國防支出將成長7%，增速降至2022年以來最低。而與此同時，從華盛頓到柏林再到東京，各國官員都在增加各自的國防開支。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據財政部周四在北京發布的報告，今年中央預算中的國防支出預計將增至1.91萬億元人民幣（約合2770億美元）。此前自2023年以來，中國每年將這一預算規模提高7.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國的國防支出預算與主要地緣政治對手相比相形見絀——至少從官方數據來看。今年早些時候，美國總統川普要求美國將2027年國防開支提高逾50%達到1.5萬億美元，不過這一史無前例地成長仍需國會批准。據五角大樓估計，中國實際的軍費支出要高於公開公佈的數字。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-81963d8e-a534-3166-9f94-29427fca081b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Lifts Defense Spending by 7% After Big Surge by Trump</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Josh Xiao、李易安.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B2026%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E6%88%90%E9%95%B77-%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B32022%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E-002331090.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 08:52:34",
